---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cookie Policy — Fimil"
  description="How Fimil uses cookies and similar technologies."
>
  <article class="py-20 dark:bg-gray-950">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <a href="/legal" class="text-sm text-fimil-600 hover:text-fimil-700 dark:text-fimil-400"
        >&larr; Legal</a
      >
      <h1 class="mt-4 font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
        Cookie Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Effective Date: March 1, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            1. What Are Cookies
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They help
            us provide and improve the Service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            2. Essential Cookies
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Required for the Service to function. These include session cookies for authentication
            and CSRF protection tokens.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            3. Analytics Cookies
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            We use privacy-respecting analytics to understand how the Service is used. No personal
            data is shared with third parties for advertising.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            4. Managing Cookies
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            You can control cookies through your browser settings. Disabling essential cookies may
            affect Service functionality.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
            5. Contact
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Questions about cookies? Contact <a
              href="mailto:privacy@fimil.dev"
              class="text-fimil-600 dark:text-fimil-400">privacy@fimil.dev</a
            >.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
